    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 关于本游戏（完整版描述）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**《恐惧低语》**是一款章节式心理恐怖游戏，每一章讲述一位与不可名状之物独处之人的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是拯救世界的史诗，而是关于那些试图守住理智、却渐渐听见某种低语的人的回忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/46f95c504be2d7c4c30064d6eda43627.poster.avif?t=1767840207\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/46f95c504be2d7c4c30064d6eda43627.webm?t=1767840207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第一章：《孤独的低语》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一位22岁的电工，被派往一座遥远的小岛。几周前，一组地质学家前往那里挖掘旧矿井，之后就再无音讯。你独自前往，抵达的那一刻，只见雾气弥漫、灯塔微亮，岛上却空无一人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只有工具、一盏煤油灯，以及逐渐加深的感觉：<strong>你并不孤单。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/e3f6ed951f20cfe5827a146526a53a8b.poster.avif?t=1767840207\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/e3f6ed951f20cfe5827a146526a53a8b.webm?t=1767840207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >洛式氛围：古老的符号、沉默的石碑与夜色中的低语</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS风格：轻度复古视觉处理，不失真实感</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由探索：线索碎片由你自行拼凑，真相掌握在手</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸环境：湿冷的树林、嘎吱作响的木屋、缓慢压迫的声音设计</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/b99b3343fbe460e617f436010da6925d.poster.avif?t=1767840207\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/b99b3343fbe460e617f436010da6925d.webm?t=1767840207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在本章中，你将体验：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索孤岛及其废弃建筑：码头、灯塔、矿井与锯木厂</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解谜：环境与叙事结合的互动谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修复设备：收集道具以恢复岛上的电力与通讯</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶矿车穿梭区域</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做出影响结局的关键选择</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/0dd60332bc347db3d6cbcf471d9c6c0d.poster.avif?t=1767840207\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/0dd60332bc347db3d6cbcf471d9c6c0d.webm?t=1767840207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你能否熬过这个夜晚，揭开令他人崩溃的真相？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是，也会成为雾中那道回音？</p>",
